dct_description_sm: Street map of Cranford Township including the Kenilworth section and a stretch of the Central Railroad of New Jersey. Legend shows schools, municipal buildings, and paved and proposed roads. There is also an index showing locations of specific municipal buildings, schools and churches.
dct_creator_sm: League of Women Voters of Cranford
